### About Me

I am a Student of General Assembly where I learned Full Stack Web Development using Ruby, Ruby on Rails, CSS, HTML5, and Javascript. I also studied Computer Science at Arizona State where I learned some Javascript Basic computer Hardware and Architecture and fundamentals of computer science. I am currently looking for employment as a junior web developer.
